    "Projected Hamiltonian with Interaction SchemeWe have introduced the interaction term (Eq. 24) in the many-body Hamiltonian, paying attention to subtleties associated with the interaction scheme.",
    "We have also discussed band projection, leading to the projected Hamiltonian in Eq. 29.",
    "In the following, we project to the central bands of TBG, i.e.",
    "8 total bands including spins and valleys, though the formalism straightforwardly generalizes to cases where a larger number of active bands are retained.",
